### -----------------------------------------------------------
### 검증: Job 목록 조회 (10건 확인)
### -----------------------------------------------------------

### Job 전체 목록
GET {{host}}/api/jobs

### -----------------------------------------------------------
### Phase 1b: Pipeline 3개 생성 + Job 매핑
### -----------------------------------------------------------

### Pipeline 1: "CI/CD Full" (선형: maven-build → docker-image-build → k8s-deploy-dev → k8s-deploy-staging)
POST {{host}}/api/pipelines
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "CI/CD Full",
  "description": "Maven 빌드 → Docker 이미지 → Dev 배포 → Staging 배포 (선형)"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("pipeline1Id", response.body.data.id);
%}

### Pipeline 1: Job 매핑 (선형 DAG)
PUT {{host}}/api/pipelines/{{pipeline1Id}}/mappings
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "jobId": {{mavenBuildId}},
    "executionOrder": 1,
    "dependsOnJobIds": []
  },
  {
    "jobId": {{dockerImageBuildId}},
    "executionOrder": 2,
    "dependsOnJobIds": [{{mavenBuildId}}]
  },
  {
    "jobId": {{k8sDeployDevId}},
    "executionOrder": 3,
    "dependsOnJobIds": [{{dockerImageBuildId}}]
  },
  {
    "jobId": {{k8sDeployStagingId}},
    "executionOrder": 4,
    "dependsOnJobIds": [{{k8sDeployDevId}}]
  }
]

### Pipeline 2: "Multi-Build Fan-out" (DAG: gradle+npm → nexus → k8s-deploy-prod)
POST {{host}}/api/pipelines
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Multi-Build Fan-out",
  "description": "Gradle/NPM 병렬 빌드 → Nexus 업로드 → Prod 배포 (DAG Fan-out)"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("pipeline2Id", response.body.data.id);
%}

### Pipeline 2: Job 매핑 (Fan-out DAG)
PUT {{host}}/api/pipelines/{{pipeline2Id}}/mappings
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "jobId": {{gradleBuildId}},
    "executionOrder": 1,
    "dependsOnJobIds": []
  },
  {
    "jobId": {{npmBuildId}},
    "executionOrder": 1,
    "dependsOnJobIds": []
  },
  {
    "jobId": {{nexusUploadId}},
    "executionOrder": 2,
    "dependsOnJobIds": [{{gradleBuildId}}, {{npmBuildId}}]
  },
  {
    "jobId": {{k8sDeployProdId}},
    "executionOrder": 3,
    "dependsOnJobIds": [{{nexusUploadId}}]
  }
]

### Pipeline 3: "Quick Deploy" (부분 선형: git-clone-build → registry-pull → k8s-deploy-dev)
POST {{host}}/api/pipelines
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Quick Deploy",
  "description": "Git Clone → Registry Pull → Dev 배포 (빠른 배포)"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("pipeline3Id", response.body.data.id);
%}

### Pipeline 3: Job 매핑 (선형)
PUT {{host}}/api/pipelines/{{pipeline3Id}}/mappings
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "jobId": {{gitCloneBuildId}},
    "executionOrder": 1,
    "dependsOnJobIds": []
  },
  {
    "jobId": {{registryPullId}},
    "executionOrder": 2,
    "dependsOnJobIds": [{{gitCloneBuildId}}]
  },
  {
    "jobId": {{k8sDeployDevId}},
    "executionOrder": 3,
    "dependsOnJobIds": [{{registryPullId}}]
  }
]

### -----------------------------------------------------------
### 검증: Pipeline 목록 조회 (3건 + Job 매핑 확인)
### -----------------------------------------------------------

### Pipeline 전체 목록
GET {{host}}/api/pipelines

### Pipeline 1 상세 (Job 4개 매핑 확인)
GET {{host}}/api/pipelines/{{pipeline1Id}}

### Pipeline 2 상세 (Job 4개, Fan-out 확인)
GET {{host}}/api/pipelines/{{pipeline2Id}}

### Pipeline 3 상세 (Job 3개 매핑 확인)
GET {{host}}/api/pipelines/{{pipeline3Id}}

### -----------------------------------------------------------
### Phase 1c: 실행 테스트
### -----------------------------------------------------------

### Job 단독 실행: maven-build
POST {{host}}/api/jobs/{{mavenBuildId}}/execute

> {%
  client.global.set("jobExecId", response.body.data.executionId);
%}

### Pipeline 1 실행: CI/CD Full (선형)
POST {{host}}/api/pipelines/{{pipeline1Id}}/execute

> {%
  client.global.set("pipeline1ExecId", response.body.data.executionId);
%}

### Pipeline 2 실행: Multi-Build Fan-out (DAG)
POST {{host}}/api/pipelines/{{pipeline2Id}}/execute

> {%
  client.global.set("pipeline2ExecId", response.body.data.executionId);
%}

### Pipeline 3 실행: Quick Deploy (부분 선형)
POST {{host}}/api/pipelines/{{pipeline3Id}}/execute

> {%
  client.global.set("pipeline3ExecId", response.body.data.executionId);
%}

### -----------------------------------------------------------
### Phase 3: 검증
### -----------------------------------------------------------

### 검증 1: Job 전체 목록 (10건)
GET {{host}}/api/jobs

### 검증 2: Pipeline 전체 목록 (3건)
GET {{host}}/api/pipelines

### -----------------------------------------------------------
### SSE 실시간 추적 (브라우저 또는 curl로 확인)
### -----------------------------------------------------------

### Pipeline 1 SSE 이벤트 스트림
### curl -N "http://localhost:8080/api/pipelines/executions/{{pipeline1ExecId}}/events"

### Pipeline 2 SSE 이벤트 스트림
### curl -N "http://localhost:8080/api/pipelines/executions/{{pipeline2ExecId}}/events"

### -----------------------------------------------------------
### Cleanup (필요 시)
### -----------------------------------------------------------

### Pipeline 삭제
# DELETE {{host}}/api/pipelines/{{pipeline1Id}}
# DELETE {{host}}/api/pipelines/{{pipeline2Id}}
# DELETE {{host}}/api/pipelines/{{pipeline3Id}}

